<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-7">
			<p class="main-head">Here at the Gary Arthur Network you can<br />register for <span style="font-weight: 800; color: #bf0000;">NCE</span> and <span style="font-weight: 800; color: #bf0000;">NCMHCE</span> workshops<br />and purchase the study programs.</p>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-5">
			<img src="/img/main-group.png" width="380px" style="margin-top: 18px;"/>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="container">
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12">
			<div class="row">
		<hr />
		<div class="col-md-6">
			<h1 style="margin-top: 0px;">Workshops</h1>
			<% @workshop = Workshop.all %>
			<p>Dr. Arthur has conducted <%= @workshop.total %> 2-day workshops since 1986. The National Counselorâ€™s Examination Workshop covers 9-study units over 2-days. The workshop covers two hour periods for each unit representing most of the questions and less time on units for fewer items on the NCE.</p>
			<p><a href="/workshops" class="btn btn-info btn-xs">Learn more...</a></p>
			<br />
			<h1 style="margin-top: 0px;">Study Programs</h1>
			<p>The Dr. Arthur Study Programs have a proven record in how to narrow the study material to the essentials. Repeatedly users have indicated that the manual content is a must for preparation. He has a knack in writing questions that are structured in the same way as the actual test. Unlike other manuals he is the single writer who has taught all the course content.</p>
			<p><a href="/studyguides" class="btn btn-info btn-xs">Learn more...</a></p>
			<div style="margin-bottom: 2em;"> &nbsp; </div>
		</div>
		<div class="col-md-6"> 
			<h1 style="font-size: 1.8em; margin-top: 0px;">Upcoming <span style="font-weight: 800; color: #bf0000;">NCE</span> Workshops</h1>
			<div id="upcoming-workshops">
				<% Workshop.all(program: "nce").upcoming.each do |w| %>
				<div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
					<div class="panel panel-default">
						<a data-toggle="collapse" class="accord" data-parent="#accordion" href="#<%= w.id %>">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<h4 class="panel-title">
									<%= format_day w.start_date %>
									<% unless w.start_date == w.end_date %>
									- <%= format_day w.end_date %>
									<% end %>
									<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down pull-right" style="color: #7adfff;"></span>
								</h4>
							</div>
						</a>
						<div id="<%= w.id %>" class="panel-collapse collapse">
							<div class="panel-body">
								<h3 style="font-weight: 800;"><%= w.venue %></h3>
								<p><%= Kramdown::Document.new(w.description).to_html %></p>
								<%= Kramdown::Document.new(w.price1).to_html %>
								<p><%= Kramdown::Document.new(w.time).to_html %></p>
								<p><strong><%= w.location %></strong><br />
									<small><%= w.address1 %>&nbsp; <%= w.city %>&nbsp; <%= w.state %>&nbsp; <%= w.zip %></small></p>
								</p>
								<a href="/admin/reservations/new" class="btn btn-success btn-xs">Reserve a seat</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				<% end %>
			<hr />
			<h1 style="font-size: 1.8em;">Upcoming <span style="font-weight: 800; color: #bf0000;">NCMHCE</span> Workshops</h1>
			<% Workshop.all(program: "ncmhce").upcoming.each do |w| %>
				<div class="panel-group" id="accordion">
					<div class="panel panel-default">
						<a data-toggle="collapse" class="accord" data-parent="#accordion" href="#<%= w.id %>">
							<div class="panel-heading">
								<h4 class="panel-title">
									<%= format_day w.start_date %>
									<% unless w.start_date == w.end_date %>
									- <%= format_day w.end_date %>
									<% end %>
									<span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down pull-right" style="color: #7adfff;"></span>
								</h4>
							</div>
						</a>
						<div id="<%= w.id %>" class="panel-collapse collapse">
							<div class="panel-body">
								<h3 style="font-weight: 800;"><%= w.venue %></h3>
								<p><%= Kramdown::Document.new(w.description).to_html %></p>
								<%= Kramdown::Document.new(w.price1).to_html %>
								<p><%= Kramdown::Document.new(w.time).to_html %></p>
								<p><strong><%= w.location %></strong><br />
									<small><%= w.address1 %>&nbsp; <%= w.city %>&nbsp; <%= w.state %>&nbsp; <%= w.zip %></small></p>
								</p>
								<a href="/admin/reservations/new" class="btn btn-success btn-xs">Reserve a seat</a>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				<% end %>
			</div>
		</div></div></div>
	</div>
</div>